			<p>An entry into the <a href='http://www.informationisbeautifulawards.com/2012/03/hall-of-fame-hollywood-challenge-winners/'>Information is Beautiful Hollywood Challenge</a>.
			
				This highly interactive web application is designed to explore some of 
				the metrics coming out of Hollywood. The tool covers over 500 films from 
				the past 5 years.
			</p>	
				
			<p>The data explorer specifically takes a neutral stance, 
				and allows the users to draw their own conclusions. 
				 There are literally thousands of possible combinations.
			</p>	
			
		
			<p>Built with lots of <a href='http://d3js.org'>d3</a> and jQuery.  
				Placed 2nd place in the interactive category.
			
